{
  "texts": [
    "-The Side Effect Resource (SIDER) 46 is a database of drugs and adverse drug reactions.",
    "The SIDER dataset contains 1427 molecular structures assembled in the DeepChem library 47 with side effects grouped in 27 system organ classes according to MedDRA classifications (Medical Dictionary for Regulatory Activities, http://www.meddra.org/).",
    "-The SMRT (Small Molecule Retention Time) dataset consists of molecules and their experimentally acquired reverse-phase chromatography retention times 48.",
    "Pure standard materials of 80,038 small molecules including metabolites, natural products, and drug-like small molecules have been measured.",
    "This dataset is much larger than the other datasets."
  ]
}